                            <comment id="67213" author="jcl" created="Sun, 22 Sep 2013 22:28:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch at  &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/7723&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/7723&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="67131" author="jlevi" created="Fri, 20 Sep 2013 16:18:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;JC is working on the patch. Assigning to James to shepherd through.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="67117" author="jamesanunez" created="Fri, 20 Sep 2013 15:24:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m tied up with HSM testing. So, I don&apos;t plan to create a patch for this test. Please create and submit the patch if you have time.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks, James&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="67100" author="jcl" created="Fri, 20 Sep 2013 11:43:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Agree: test 9a is buggy 0x00000001 must be replaced by 0x00000009 (ARCHIVED + EXIST). If you do the patch please do also following change:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;replace need2clients by needclients which will take a client count as arg&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;test_9a should be changed to use needclients 3&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;need2clients should be changed to use needclients 2&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;I can do the patch&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
